-- Saint Gobain Recovery Varies by Country, Industry, Chief Executive Says
-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 2010-10-25T05:52:53Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-25/saint-gobain-recovery-varies-by-country-industry-chief-executive-says.html
Cie. de Saint-Gobain SA’s recovery
is variable according to country and industry, Chief Executive
Officer Pierre-Andre de Chalendar said on BFM radio station.  The recovery, which is taking place everywhere, hasn’t yet
led to activity returning to pre-crisis levels, he said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
